    <p class="text-center mb-5">Understanding your body and reproductive system is essential for making informed decisions about your health.</p>
    
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h2>What is Sexual & Reproductive Health?</h2>
        <p>Sexual and reproductive health encompasses the physical, mental, and social well-being related to all aspects of the reproductive system. It addresses the reproductive processes, functions, and systems at all stages of life.</p>
        <p>Good sexual and reproductive health means:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Having accurate information about your body</li>
          <li>Access to safe, effective, and affordable contraception</li>
          <li>Freedom from sexual violence and coercion</li>
          <li>Access to comprehensive healthcare services</li>
          <li>The ability to have a satisfying and safe sex life</li>
          <li>The capability to reproduce and the freedom to decide if, when, and how often to do so</li>
        </ul>
